item.title: The Lion King
item.description: Katie and Bridget frantically try to read the closed captioning words to "The Circle of Life" as they re-watch Katie's favorite animated movie: The Lion King! It's basically just Hamlet with some cartoon lions - and a little bit of Bambi tossed in there too! Come along as we meet Simba, a lion cub destined to be king who goes through TRAUMA as he gets gaslighted into thinking he killed his dad Mufasa... Feed: https://feeds.buzzsprout.com/1188341.rss
